Title: Astral Runner- The Choosen One
Author: অমর আগারওয়াল
Summary:
Summary of the Book

The real and the surreal clash in this fantasy novel. Varish Sanghvi’s world as a chartered accountant is ripped apart when divinity calls him to action. His mission will be a dangerous and invigorating journey. He must travel through an unbelievable astral zone, treading treacherous pathways to discover the truth. But will he brave this mysterious quest? He will need to be on guard at all times, poised on the edge of a blade. If he does, he must accept the gauntlet thrown at him from Hades, the evil netherworld, where death lurks behind every corner. Varish is caught between life and death, divinity and evil in his quest to be the Chosen One!
